\": 5360}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5381, \"to\": 5390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is clear to me that any attempts of reform at Wada have fallen short, and there are still deeply rooted, systemic problems that prove detrimental to the integrity of international sports and athletes' right to fair competition, time and time again.\\\"\", \"from\": 5393, \"to\": 5646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any attempts\", \"from\": 5417, \"to\": 5429}, {\"ngram\": \"reform\", \"from\": 5433, \"to\": 5439}, {\"ngram\": \"Wada\", \"from\": 5443, \"to\": 5447}, {\"ngram\": \"deeply rooted, systemic problems\", \"from\": 5487, \"to\": 5519}, {\"ngram\": \"the integrity\", \"from\": 5546, \"to\": 5559}, {\"ngram\": \"international sports\", \"from\": 5563, \"to\": 5583}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' right\", \"from\": 5588, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"fair competition\", \"from\": 5607, \"to\": 5623}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 5625, \"to\": 5629}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 5634, \"to\": 5638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Wednesday, seven-time US gold medallist Katie Ledecky said: \\\"Athletes want transparency.\", \"from\": 5648, \"to\": 5739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5673, \"end\": 5680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U.S._Gold\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"US gold\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U.S._Gold\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U.S._Gold\"}, {\"begin\": 5691, \"end\": 5704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 5651, \"to\": 5660}, {\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5720}, {\"ngram\": \"transparency\", \"from\": 5726, \"to\": 5738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They want further answers to the questions that remain.\", \"from\": 5740, \"to\": 5795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"further answers\", \"from\": 5750, \"to\": 5765}, {\"ngram\": \"the questions\", \"from\": 5769, \"to\": 5782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to see some change for the future so that you do not have to ask us that question.\\\"\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some change\", \"from\": 5811, \"to\": 5822}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 5827, \"to\": 5837}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5869, \"to\": 5871}, {\"ngram\": \"that question\", \"from\": 5872, \"to\": 5885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was similar sentiment from Australian Zac Stubblety-Cook, whose 200m breaststroke world record was beaten by Qin last year.\", \"from\": 5889, \"to\": 6018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5922, \"end\": 5932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9975412667029109, \"rank\": 0.002159856665488659, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 6004, \"end\": 6007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"score\": 0.580116920620546, \"rank\": 0.6330048615081335, \"text\": \"Qin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"similar sentiment\", \"from\": 5899, \"to\": 5916}, {\"ngram\": \"whose 200m breaststroke world record\", \"from\": 5953, \"to\": 5989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It feels like [Wada has] failed and that's the truth,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 6020, \"to\": 6084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wada\", \"from\": 6036, \"to\": 6040}, {\"ngram\": \"the truth\", \"from\": 6064, \"to\": 6073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I absolutely believe in clean sport and I hope that this is a clean Games.\", \"from\": 6086, \"to\": 6161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"clean sport\", \"from\": 6111, \"to\": 6122}, {\"ngram\": \"a clean Games\", \"from\": 6147, \"to\": 6160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's obviously disappointing to hear about the positive tests of 23 athletes; in some cases multiple positives.\", \"from\": 6162, \"to\": 6273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the positive tests\", \"from\": 6205, \"to\": 6223}, {\"ngram\": \"23 athletes\", \"from\": 6227, \"to\": 6238}, {\"ngram\": \"some cases\", \"from\": 6243, \"to\": 6253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, for me, finding out that you are racing someone who was one of those athletes is disappointing.\\\"\", \"from\": 6274, \"to\": 6375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 6319, \"to\": 6326}, {\"ngram\": \"those athletes\", \"from\": 6342, \"to\": 6356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Impartial news + intelligent debate All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 6377, \"to\": 6434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Impartial news + intelligent debate\", \"from\": 6377, \"to\": 6412}, {\"ngram\": \"All rights\", \"from\": 6413, \"to\": 6423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2026 Associated Newspapers Limited.\", \"from\": 6435, \"to\": 6472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a9\", \"from\": 6435, \"to\": 6436}]}]}"